# Static build for Vercel — ship only the frontend. Excluding the Python code
# ensures Vercel does NOT turn api/*.py into serverless functions (which can't
# run this app). The odds/bracket/teams are precomputed into
# frontend/public/data/*.json by scripts/build_data.py.
api/
scripts/
*.py
requirements.txt
.venv/
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
render.yaml
fly.toml
live_results.csv
.cache_results.csv*
